setarenaboss bossName: Set the arena boss by name.
additem item amount: Add a specified item to the player's inventory. Use /finditemid to get valid item names.
additem item: Add a specified item to the player's inventory. Use /finditemid to get valid item names.
addrangeofitems item range amount: Add a range of items to the player's inventory. Use /finditemid to get valid item names.
addrangeofitems item range: Add a range of items to the player's inventory. Use /finditemid to get valid item names.
addstat stat amount: Add a specified amount to a player's stat. Use /printallstats to get valid stat names.
addpermenentstatbonus stat amount: Add a permanent bonus to a player's stat. Use /printallstats to get valid stat names.
setstat stat amount: Set a player's stat to a specific amount. Use /printallstats to get valid stat names.
getstat stat: Get the current value of a specified stat. Use /printallstats to get valid stat names.
skipday days: Skip a specified number of days in the game.
addtime time: Add a specified amount of time to the current day.
settime hour: Set the current time to a specific hour.
setseason season: Set the current season in the game. Use /printallseasons to get valid season names.
setday day: Set the current day in the game.
setdayspeed speed: Set the speed of the day cycle.
setbirthday season day: Set the player's birthday. Use /printallseasons to get valid season names.
enabledaycycle enable: Enable or disable the day cycle.
teleport sceneName: Teleport the player to a specified scene. Use /printallscenes to get valid scene names.
addmoney amount: Add money to the player's inventory.
setmaxfoodstats amount: Set the maximum food stats for the player.
setuiactive active: Set the UI active or inactive.
setuiactivebutactionbar active: Set the UI active or inactive except for the action bar.
resetcharacterprogress progress: Reset the progress for a specified character.
setcharacterprogress progress: Set the progress for a specified character.
resetworldprogress progress: Reset the progress for the game world.
setworldprogress progress: Set the progress for the game world.
setrelationship npc amount: Set the relationship level with a specified NPC.
skiptonpccycle npc cycle: Skip to a specified NPC cycle.
skiptoworldquest breakpoint: Skip to a specified world quest.
skiptoworldquestwithergate breakpoint: Skip to a specified world quest in Withergate.
skiptoworldquestnelvari breakpoint: Skip to a specified world quest in Nelvari.
skiptoworldepilogue breakpoint: Skip to a specified world epilogue.
addexp profession amount: Add experience points to a specified profession. Use /printallprofessions to get valid profession names.
setexp profession amount: Set the experience points for a specified profession. Use /printallprofessions to get valid profession names.
startquest questname: Start a specified quest. Use /printallbbquests to get valid quest names.
abandonquest questname: Abandon a specified quest. Use /printallbbquests to get valid quest names.
setbulletinboardquest questname1 questna: Set a specified bulletin board quest. Use /printallbbquests to get valid quest names.
sendmail mailName: Send a mail to the player. Use /printallmail to get valid mail names.
getworldquestskipwithergatebreakpoints b: Print all quests skipped by worldquestskipwithergate up to a specified breakpoint.
getworldquestskipepiloguebreakpoints bre: Print all quests initiated by worldquestskipepilogue up to a specified breakpoint.
getworldquestskipnelvaribreakpoints brea: Print all quests skipped by worldquestskipnelvari up to a specified breakpoint.
getworldquestskipbreakpoints breakpoint: Print all quests skipped by worldquestskip up to a specified breakpoint.
printallscenes: Print all scenes available for use in commands.
printallseasons: Print all seasons available for use in commands.
printallprofessions: Print all professions available for use in commands.
printallstats: Print all stats available for use in commands.
printallmail: Print all mail available for use in commands.
printallbbquests: Print all bulletin board quests available for use in commands.
printallnpcs: Print all NPCs in the game.
additembyid itemId amount: Add an item to the player's inventory by item ID and amount.
additembyid itemId: Add an item to the player's inventory by item ID.
finditemid itemName: Search for an item by name.
saveallitems: Save all items to a file.
adddevitems: Add developer-specific items to the player's inventory.
resetpermanentstatbonuses: Reset all permanent stat bonuses for the current character.
skipday: Skip one day in the game.
pausetime: Pause the progression of time in the game.
unpausetime: Resume the progression of time in the game.
resetmoney: Reset the player's money to zero.
resetalldecoration: Reset all decorations in the game.
unlockmines: Unlock all mines in the game.
lockmines: Lock all mines in the game.
resetrelationships: Reset all relationships in the game.
getrelationships: Get all relationships in the game.
setdaya: Set the current day to type A.
setdayb: Set the current day to type B.
setdayrain: Set the current day to rain.
setdaylightsnow: Set the current day to light snow.
setdaygloomyrain: Set the current day to gloomy rain.
setdayfoggy: Set the current day to foggy.
setdaywindy: Set the current day to windy.
setdayseasonalparticle: Set the current day to a seasonal particle effect.
printquestlog: Print out the current quests in your quest log.
printallarenabosses: Print out all the arena boss names.
noclip: Toggles noclip on/off depending on the current state. Use /noclip true|false for specific control.
godmode: Toggles godmode on/off depending on the current state. Use /godmode true|false for specific control.
